NAME
    Framework::Redmash - Framework for quickly setting up a webpage/website
    using Template Toolkit

VERSION
    Version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
        package MyProject;

        use Framework::Redmash name => 'myproject';

        # Then, from the commandline ...
    
        redmash setup
        redmash about

DESCRIPTION
    This is beta!

    Framework::Redmash is an attempt to take the drudgery out of setting up
    a website. After you run 'setup' you should have a basic assets/
    directory, including a standard frame .tt and some baseline .css

